This paper is primarily focused on improving object detection using image context, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also utilizes a pre-trained dependency model and optimization techniques, which are common in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the reduction of false alarms, which is a topic in information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
